There is no problem with swapping CHR ROM on an MMC3. The problem is with swapping PRG ROM. It's nothing that a little bit of rearrangement with the help of Doppelganger's disassembly can't solve, but it may be beyond the abilities of someone who admits that (s)he "never programmed anything in 6502 assembler".<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Mon Oct 25, 2010 2:36 pm</p><hr />
